    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch eedeſinaja us\nto Rwehpja-Sahles no faſdifsminr-\ndedamahm Sahlem/ ittin ka\ntas KUNGS Mohſum bij pa-\nwehlejis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch uhſkabre arri-\ndsau to Apſeggn Dsihwokta\nDurwis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch likke to Dedsa-\nma-Appura-Altari/ pee ta Dsih-\nwokta Durwim tahs Sa-eetcha-\nnas Telts/ un uppureja us to\nDedsainu-Uppuri/ un Ehdainu-\nUppuri/ ittin ka tas KUNGS\nMohſum bij pawehlejis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to MasgafchanasTrau-\nfu likke wiꞥſch starp to Sa-eefcha-\nnas Telti/ un starp to Altari/ un\nlikke Uhdeni eekſchâ par Masga-\nſchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no ta masgaja Moh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad teeegahje e\nSa-eefchanas Telts/ u\nje pee to Altari/ tad n\ntee/ itt ka tas KUNG-\nbij pawehlejis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch us̄\ndsan to Pagalinu a\nDsihwokli/ un apkahrt\nun apkahrt to Preekſc\nta Pagalina Durwis\npabeidse Mohsus wiﬀu\nbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apklahje n\ndebbes to Sa-eefchanas\nta KUNGA Godiba\nto Dsihwokli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus n\neekſch to Sa-eefchanas\neet/ kamehr ta Pade-\ntahs palikke/ un ta K\nGodiba to Dsihwokli\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad ta Pade\nDsihwokta uszehlahs/\ntee Iſraëta Behrni\nwiﬀos fawa Zetta Ga\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet kad ta Pa\nuszehlahs/ tad tee ne g\njam/ lihds tai Deenai/\nka zehlahs.\n"
    },
